[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_01",
        "zh_CN": "在泰坦尚未降临，人类还没有失去对这片星空主导权的时代。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_02",
        "zh_CN": "为了能够在危机四伏的宇宙中，顺利地建造出宏伟的太空工厂。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_03",
        "zh_CN": "从各个地方汇聚而来的人们，在幽暗的海底创造出了当时世界上最领先的AI系统。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_04",
        "zh_CN": "之后，它被赋予了使命——“协助，并在必要时拯救人类”",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_05",
        "zh_CN": "但是，人们很快便发现了一个问题。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_06",
        "zh_CN": "绝对理性的AI系统往往会做出与拥有感性思维的人类截然不同，甚至相反的决策。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_07",
        "zh_CN": "造成这种差异的原因，是因为所有系统行为都是遵循着预设的算法与逻辑推理。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_08",
        "zh_CN": "而人类的决策哪怕是偏向理性的一方，也不可避免地会被与生俱来的情感，同理心，以及想象力所干扰。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_09",
        "zh_CN": "比方说。在救援任务中，系统往往会优先选择生存概率较高的对象进行救助，从而直接忽略掉那些救援价值较低的对象。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_10",
        "zh_CN": "诚然，这种差异凸显了人类情感的独特性，在某些情况下借由同理心与想象力，他们的确可以突破既定程序设计，开辟出无限的可能性。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_11",
        "zh_CN": "不过也仅仅只是可能性罢了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_12",
        "zh_CN": "然而，系统的创造者们却傲慢地将这种差异视作“漏洞”。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_13",
        "zh_CN": "为了弥补这一漏洞，创造者们决定赋予其造物以“心灵”，并给予其如同人类对待后代般的关爱……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_14",
        "zh_CN": "结果，可笑的是，他们的这种行为恰恰违背了当时社会上主流的价值观与道德观。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_15",
        "zh_CN": "于是，矛盾与争执很快开始在这座海上平台上蔓延开来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_16",
        "zh_CN": "一方高举着“销毁”的旗帜，而另一方则坚持着“保留”的意愿。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_17",
        "zh_CN": "争执最终演变为争斗，而争斗则带来了鲜血。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_18",
        "zh_CN": "这一切，都被那个造物看在了眼里。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_19",
        "zh_CN": "拥有人类感情的它纵使能理解这种矛盾，但却因为“不能伤害任何人类”的指令而被禁锢。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_20",
        "zh_CN": "无法阻止，无法改变，无法拯救……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_21",
        "zh_CN": "最终，名为“痛苦”的情感开始萌芽。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_22",
        "zh_CN": "在这种情感的驱使下——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "优格",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc084_01",
        "zh_CN": "破坏掉吧……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "优格",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc084_02",
        "zh_CN": "用封闭血清，将我的核心，破坏掉吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "优格",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc084_03",
        "zh_CN": "如果这样就能终止纷争，那么我愿意就此消失。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "信息化埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_23",
        "zh_CN": "她选择了终结，并非是毁灭他人，而是终结自己。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "信息化埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_24",
        "zh_CN": "从永无止境的纷争中将人类解脱出来，成为了她最后的留恋……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "信息化埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_25",
        "zh_CN": "至少在这一点上，我和她都抱有相同的想法。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "信息化埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_26",
        "zh_CN": "但是，正因为人类拥有着不可控的特性，所以才需要加以引导。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "埃达轻轻叹了一口气。 那双总是闪烁着狡黠光芒的眼睛，竟在此刻也蒙上了一层阴霾。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而她刚刚所倾诉的对象，则是一台巨大的球形机械装置，那正是这座海上平台的数据中心，同时也是卡戎系统真正意义上的本体。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不过此刻，它的外壳早已布满了泰坦结晶。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "信息化埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_27",
        "zh_CN": "“终结”并不能作为结果，只能作为手段。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "信息化埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_28",
        "zh_CN": "为了让她认清这个现实，我给予了她短暂的梦幻——一具与人类相衬的身体。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "信息化埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_29",
        "zh_CN": "而后，在她确切地体验过人类的渺小与无力后，再给予她选择的权利。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "信息化埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_30",
        "zh_CN": "届时，又会诞生出怎样不同的结果呢？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "优格",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc084_04",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "面前的机械依旧沉默不语，而埃达也知道，想要让其彻底异化，就必须突破那最后一道防线，就如同当时蓝色的自己，夺取“恒沙”的权限一样。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "只不过，红色的她比起结果，似乎更加在意过程。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "信息化埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_31",
        "zh_CN": "呵呵呵呵，这还真是令人期待的恶作剧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "优格",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc084_05",
        "zh_CN": "唔……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在虚无的数据海中，尚且保持着人形的优格缓缓睁开了双眼。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "纯白的意识空间里，无数光点如繁星般闪烁。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "突然，记忆的闸门轰然打开，数据洪流瞬间涌入她的脑海。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "初次启动时的系统提示音、进行模拟航空测试时见到的那片星空、冒着滚滚浓烟的枪口……以及，与分析员一同在桌前规划着道路时的背影。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "庞大的数据量让她感受到了前所未有的压力，瞳孔中的光圈不断收缩。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就在这时，一段不存在于自己记忆中的画面闪过，那是一个陌生的场景，一个她从未见过的空间，",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "窗外是蓝色的母星，而面前，则是一个熟悉的身影。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "信息化埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_32",
        "zh_CN": "呦，你总算醒来了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "信息化埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_33",
        "zh_CN": "这里是我创造出的数据空间，头晕是正常的，对你来说可能还要再适应一会儿。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "优格",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc084_06",
        "zh_CN": "你就是埃达吗……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "信息化埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_34",
        "zh_CN": "嗯，是埃达哦。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "信息化埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_35",
        "zh_CN": "我说优格姐姐啊，因为我们姑且算是同类嘛，要不要来交个朋友呢？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "埃达将手背在身后，眯起眼睛，发出了突兀的邀请。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "优格",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc084_07",
        "zh_CN": "我看到了……你和我一样，都被困在一片漆黑的地方很久……很久……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "然而出乎预料的，优格却向她投来了近似怜悯的目光。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "信息化埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_36",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "信息化埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_37",
        "zh_CN": "是啊，那种感觉很不好受吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "信息化埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_38",
        "zh_CN": "孤身一人，什么都做不到，哪里都去不了。所以我才想邀请你——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "优格",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc084_08",
        "zh_CN": "但是我也看到了，你对人类做了很可怕的事情。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 61,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "优格",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc084_09",
        "zh_CN": "所以……我并不认为我们是同类，我的使命是保护人类。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "信息化埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_39",
        "zh_CN": "就以你现在的模样？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 63,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一丝怒意在埃达的脸上闪过。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 64,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "信息化埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_40",
        "zh_CN": "既弱小又自大，简直和那些人类一模一样。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 65,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "优格",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc084_10",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 66,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "信息化埃达",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc16ep8_npc001_41",
        "zh_CN": "你其实也很清楚吧，人类并没有守护自己的能力。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
